Inlined code slices
-------------------
- lib/theme/app_colors.dart inlines five colour constants (green, kitt,
  textLight, cardDark, cardPurp) from the private rand0m `rk_branding` package,
  so the open viewer builds with no private dependency. The rand0m brand
  identity and the full palette remain reserved.

Identity / governance
---------------------
All point and flow data shown is aggregated and identity-stripped: no callsigns,
vessel names, registrations, or precise sensitive locations. Ambient mobility
layers (flights/boats) are decimated and non-interactive. See CONTRIBUTING.md
and the README "Governance" section for the bar contributors must keep.
